# Runtime-downloaded YOLOE weights + MobileCLIP text encoder — NOT bundled. They
# are AGPL/large and get pulled into the satellite's working dir on first detect
# (the user-install model, see objects.py / the setup card). Never commit them.
# NOTE: mobileclip_blt.ts is a TorchScript file (.ts), NOT TypeScript — match it
# by name, never use a blanket *.ts (that would ignore the UI source).
*.pt
/mobileclip*.ts

# uv venv + Python caches (also covered by the repo-root .gitignore; explicit here).
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.egg-info/
